snippet.title: Disney Magical World 2: My Happy Life Enchanted Edition
snippet.description:
Disney Magical World 2: Enchanted Edition  for the Nintendo Switch™ will be available on 2nd December 2021 in Southeast Asia! 

With a letter invitation, you become a resident of the dream and magical world where Mickey and Friends live! Go out with your Disney friends and take part in various events such as shopping, making clothes and furniture, fishing, birthday parties, and dance parties! Watch the trailer to find out more!
